ww.cbr.com/cci-penn-murphy-talk-avatars-hero-worship-marvel-movies/|archivedate=September 13, 2018|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"CastPay\">{{cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/marvel-moolah-robert-downey-jr-avengers-iron-man-324639|title=Marvel Moolah: Robert Downey Jr. 'Avengers' Pay Set to Hit $50 Million|last=Belloni|first=Matthew|work=[[The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=May 15, 2012|accessdate=October 11, 2018|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/735rCU3kB?url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/marvel-moolah-robert-downey-jr-avengers-iron-man-324639|archivedate=October 11, 2018|url-status=live|df=mdy-all}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"EndgameTitleReveal\">{{cite web|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/entertainthis/2018/12/07/avengers-endgame-watch-first-trailer-marvels-anticipated-film/2212076002/|title=It's finally here! Watch the first trailer for Marvel's newly titled 'Avengers: Endgame'|last=Truitt|first=Brian|work=[[USA Today]]|date=December 7, 2018|accessdate=December 7, 2018|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/74UMYKsjQ?url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/entertainthis/2018/12/07/avengers-endgame-watch-first-trailer-marvels-anticipated-film/2212076002/|archivedate=December 7, 2018|url-status=live|df=mdy-all}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Empire100Movies\">{{cite web|url=https://empireonline.com/movies/features/best-movies/|title=The 100 Greatest Movies|work=[[Empire (film magazine)|Empire]]|date=March 20, 2018|accessdate=March 21, 2019|archiveurl=http://www.webcitation.org/772od7jiQ|archivedate=March 21, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"PhaseOne\">{{cite web|url=http://collider.com/mcu-timeline-explained/|title=MCU Timeline Explained: From Infinity Stones to Infinity War and Beyond|last=Trumbore|first=Dave|publisher=[[Collider (website)|Collider]]|date=May 1, 2018|access-date=July 5, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180706021810/http://collider.com/mcu-timeline-explained/|archive-date=July 6, 