d to keep track of some things that the writers and filmmakers of one movie were doing anyway and we started to track them and realized that we could utilize those later down the line. That's how the Cosmic Cube came about; what started as a little seed would grow and grow and grow to ''The Avengers''.|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6BtAmQRDf?url=http://movieline.com/2012/04/30/kevin-feige-on-avengers-marvel-universe-building-and-the-legacy-of-elektra/ |archivedate=November 3, 2012 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"ParamountVariety\">{{cite web|last=Stewart|first=Andrew|title=Paramount's Super Payoff for 'Iron Man 3'|url=https://variety.com/2013/film/news/iron-man-3-paramount-disney-1200479325/|accessdate=July 27, 2013|work=[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]]|date=May 10, 2013|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6RRfVkmab?url=http://variety.com/2013/film/news/iron-man-3-paramount-disney-1200479325/|archivedate=July 30, 2014|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"CraveOnline3\">{{cite web|url=http://www.craveonline.com/film/interviews/601057-exclusive-interview-kevin-feige-on-thor-and-marvels-future/2|title=Exclusive Interview: Kevin Feige on Thor and Marvel\u2019s Future|author=Bibbiani, William|publisher=[[CraveOnline]]|date=November 8, 2013|accessdate=November 9, 2013|quote=It is. I don't know when we'll actually divulge that necessarily, but it's the space stone.}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"EmpirePodcast\">{{cite web|date=April 30, 2012 |last=Plumb |first=All |title=Kevin Feige Avengers Spoiler Podcast |url=https://empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=33806 |work=[[Empire (film magazine)|Empire]] |format=audio at 02:09 |accessdate=May 2, 2012 |quote=All you need is one person in the back of the theater to go, 'Oh, it's Thanos!' for people to start going, 'Who's...? Oh, that must mean something, who's that?' and they start to learn and they start to dig deeper. |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6BtArSTQn?url=http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?N